Welcome To Kaima Studio Empire

Kaima Studio Empire is a boutique photography and videography media agency that is equipped with modern equipment, media experts, creative ideas, and technical know-how. We specialise in professional portraits, picture framing, corporate headshots, wedding photography, event photography, product photography, 360-degree photos and videos, video production, training and more.

We deliver first-class, high-quality and affordable services to individuals, professionals, artists, models, families, businesses, brands and corporate organisations in Nigeria.

Wedding Photography

We capture every beautiful moment of your wedding – the laughs, hugs, emotions, tears, kisses and more. Our style of pre-wedding and wedding photography is natural, unique and timeless.

Portrait Photography

Our ultra-modern equipment, knowledge of lighting and how to strike a perfect pose help us to achieve the best portrait shots. We excel at studio, outdoor, home and location shoots.

Corporate Headshots

We specialise in different types of headshots for websites, social media, marketing collaterals and more. We capture creative headshots that showcase your personality, profession and style.

Traditional Marriage Photography

Capturing timeless moments of love and tradition, our lens weaves the story of your cherished union in every frame.

Product Photography

We capture realistic images of your products, be it food, drinks, fashion goods, packaged products, beauty and lifestyle products, electronics, artworks, household items and many more.

Events Photography

We provide event photography and videography services for special occasions, weddings, birthdays, parties, fashion shows, exhibitions, trade shows, concerts and general corporate events.

Video Production & Film Making

Are you looking to create impactful and engaging contents for your business or organisation? We create mind-blowing videos, short films, animations and graphics that can inspire your audience.

Picture Frames

We create high-quality picture frames, and we deliver only the best to all states in Nigeria.

Costume Wears

We have high-quality costume wears up for rentals, varieties of them to give our customers the best studio and photographic experience.

Training

We provide one-on-one and group training for anyone who is looking to improve their skills in digital photography, studio photography, photo retouching, cinematography and film making.

Our Photography Portfolios

If you are looking for creative experts who can capture and document your weddings, events, corporate shoots and personal portraits in a unique and timeless manner, Kaima Studio Empire offers you a delightful and stress-free experience.
